high_descs: Move to the vanity on your left.
Pick up the pen on the vanity to the left of the mug.
Turn around and go to the dresser to the right of the black table.
Open up the top dresser drawer and put the pen inside the drawer.
Turn left and go back to the vanity.
Pick up the pen to the right of the mug.
Turn around and move back to the dresser.
Open up the top dresser drawer and put the pen inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens inside the top dresser drawer.

high_descs: Walk past the table that is on your left and then turn left to walk up to the built-in counter.
Pick up the pen that is on the counter to the left of the coffee mug.
Turn around, hanging a right to come back into the bedroom area, then walk over to the television stand that is on your left.
Place the pen in the top drawer of the television stand and close the drawer.
Turn to the left, walk past the table, turning left when you reach the end of it, and walk up to the counter again.
Pick up the remaining pen that is lying on the counter.
Turn around, walk forward, hanging a right in between the table and wall, and walk back over to the television stand.
Place the pen in the top drawer of the television stand, with the other pen.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens in the drawer of the television stand.

high_descs: Turn left then head towards the door, turn left then head towards the bathroom counter.
From the counter pick up the pen on the left side of the cup.
Turn around then head towards the table, turn right then head towards the green chair, then turn left to face the television.
Place the pen into the top drawer on the left side of the white chest, then close the door.
Turn left then head towards the door, turn left then head towards the bathroom counter.
From the counter pick up the pen next to the credit cards.
Turn around then head towards the table, turn right then head towards the green chair, then turn left to face the television.
Place the pen into the top drawer next to the other other one, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two pens into the top drawer of the white cabinet.
